snippet.title: ART IS RIFLE - The First 50 Minutes of Gameplay (Playthrough / Walkthrough) No Commentary
snippet.description:
Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2486730/ART_IS_RIFLE/
Available on Epic Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/art-is-rifle-897224

ART IS RIFLE is an open-world, FPS puzzle game with rhythmic bullets and psychedelic art styles. Powered by Unreal Engine 5 and much passion.

Discord: https://discord.gg/EmStxWP78e
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArmanPakan
My Website: https://www.codepsyche.net/
